  <metadata>
    <name>Creux du Van</name>
    <desc>A soaring cliff in the shape of a horseshoe – always recognisable, utterly unforgettable! To reach the astonishing rock arena of Creux du Van, leave Noiraigue on the legendary &quot;14 Contours Trail&quot;, the most physically challenging section of this hike. A breathtaking vista awaits you at the summit, before you take the &quot;Single&quot; path to return to your starting point.</desc>
    <time>2026-04-28T18:07:31+02:00</time>
